Optimize the publishing layout; 
01- The excessive number of functional buttons in the top bar - the addition boxes are not lightweight, and the text part lacks de-lineation. The "insert" section is not effectively utilized. The proportion of the "add topic" function is too large, and there is redundant duplication in the "add merchant/place" section.
02- Integrate the functions in the top bar such as "save" and "publish" into the bottom - simplify the overall design, remove lines - remove "insert" and directly buttonize "merchant/place," "dish," and "topic" - unify the design of the bottom navigation bar.
